snippet.title: Ambition Record Gameplay | Xbox One
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Ambition Record on Xbox One (shown here), Xbox Series X, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, and Switch.

If you're fond of PS1-era RPGs then Ambition Record is here to bring you back to the good old days and it's quite charming to boot. Full review - https://videochums.com/review/ambition-record
